      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. but it feels like there's a bit of a contradiction there. if we let every group opt out of mandates based on their own beliefs, doesn't the \"rule of law\" eventually just fall apart? like, how can you have a functioning secular state if laws are essentially optional for anyone with a religious objection?",
